<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Chihowa okcha̱ya a̱hli ƲIT162</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chihowa okcha̱ya a̱hli
 Ʋba ish binili ma!
 Chim okla puta i̱ hullot
 Ish apelahanchashke.

[V2]
 Chi̱ holitopa Chisʋs mʋt
 Okla moma i̱ hullot
 Ilap im issish hanta mʋt
 Yanʋllit ilbʋsha tok.

[V3]
 Micha ik sa peso kia
 A̱ yimma chi̱ hokʋto
 Holitopa he mak oke,
 Ahanchi tok mak oke.

[V4]
 Himak a̱ hatak puta ma!
 Ohoyo puta moma
 Micha ʋlla puta momʋt
 Anukfillit ke pisa.

[V5]
 Chihowa im ʋlla puta
 Iba fokʋt a̱ya hosh
 Saion itʋnahʋt a̱shʋt
 Yukpa ka ona lashke.

[V6]
 Momʋt ho minti, ahanchi;
 Ʋba yakni okhissa
 Klaist ʋt chin tiwa chi̱ hoka
 Momʋt hʋsh chukowashke.

[V7]
 Mikma ʋba holitopa
 I̱ Mi̱ko Chihowa ya̱
 Ish pisa na, Ʋm ʋlla ma!
 Chim acha he mak oke.</lyrics>
<aka>Love of Christ to his People.</aka>
<hymn_number>162</hymn_number>
<author>Cyrus Kingsbury</author>
</song>